      "role": "user",
      "content": "therapy? i dont think anyone can fix this. it's not just being sad. it's like the entire foundation of my life is just... empty. there's no \"getting through it.\" there's just this massive hole where my future used to be. it feels like i'm just waiting for something to end.",
